<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Kyrie eleyson.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Christe eleyson.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Christe eleyson.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Christe eleyson.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Kyrie eleyson.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Kyrie eleyson.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Kyrie eleyson.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Dominus vobiscum. </foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Et cum spiritu tuo.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Per omnia s&aelig;cula s&aelig;culorum. </foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Amen.</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>Epistolia akabau ta</hi></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Deo gratias.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Dominus vobiscum. </foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Et cum spiritu tuo.</foreign></p>
