<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Gloria tibi, Domine.</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>Ebanjeliyoa akabau ta</hi></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Laus tibi, Christe.</foreign></p>
