<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Suscipiat Donimus sacrificium de manibus tuis, ad laudem, et gloriam nominis sui, ad utilitatem quoque nostram, totius que Ecclesi&aelig; su&aelig; sant&aelig;.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Amen.</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>Prefaziyoa esaten danian</hi></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Per omnia s&aelig;cula s&aelig;culorum. </foreign></p>
