<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Sursum corda. R. Habemus ad Dominum.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Gratias agamus Domino Deo nostro.</foreign></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>R.</hi></foreign><foreign> Dignum et justum est.</foreign></p>
<p><hi rend='Bold'>Pater nosterra esan azkero</hi></p>
<p><foreign><hi rend='Bold'>S.</hi></foreign><foreign> Et ne nos inducas in tentacionen.</foreign></p>
